# Troubleshooting 3rd party NLU Providers

Occasionally you may run into problems using NLU integrations from other providers. Following is some tips to help with these issues.

## IBM Watson

## How to resolve max workspace limit issue?

We see this error only for Watson NLU, when the max workspace limit is reached on the account.

Follow the steps to resolve this issue:

1. Login to cloud.ibm.com:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Expand the Navigation Menu and click on Resource List in the left panel:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Click on Watson Integration:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Click on Launch Watson Assistant, it opens up a new window.

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Click on Skills tab and delete the unused skill.

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Delete skill:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mP4//8/AwAI/AL+eMSysAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==)

Select the skill. Click on the Delete link in the Context menu.This opens a popup. Enter the text as DELETE and click on Save. This successfully deletes the Skill.
